  "texts": [
    "The aim is to create a concept map for adaptive learning to provide an educational advisor for students.",
    "Alinani et al. (2016) proposed a heterogeneous educational resource recommender system based on user preferences 24.",
    "This system not only meets users' needs but also reduces some of the problems of most recommender systems, such as cold start.",
    "To do this, the system recommends the user on the recent request process and learns from the user's behavior in the process.",
    "A key point of this is that each recommended resource is assigned a weight, which is calculated based on the user's response."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Alinani et al. (2016) proposed a heterogeneous educational resource recommender system based on user preferences 24."
  ]
